item.title: The Gathering Testimony: Joanna Gaines
item.description:
The Gathering Testimony: Joanna Gaines

Baylor University graduate Joanna Gaines, co-host of HGTV's "Fixer Upper," shares how following God's direction -- even while questioning it -- has led to experiences beyond her wildest dreams. Credits: Produced by Robert Fuller (http://www.fullwritecreative.com) of Antioch Community Church (http://www.antiochcc.com) in Waco, Texas, for The Gathering, held at McLane Stadium on Palm Sunday, March 29, 2015.
